santiago de cali    often shortened to cali is the main city municipality and capital of the  valle del cauca  a department in western  colombia  with a population of 2316654 hab  santiago de cali is the third largest city in  colombia  it is a reference point inside colombia because of its industrial and commercial development and has one of the fastest growing economies in the country because of its geographical location cali was founded on july 25th in 1536 by the spanish conqueror  sebastián de belalcázar
